<p>This document provides a technical overview of the GigaCheck system, an =
LLM-generated content detection framework built on Mistral-7B-v0.3. GigaChe=
ck performs two distinct tasks: document-level classification (binary human=
/AI labels) and fine-grained detection (character-level interval localizati=
on of AI-generated text spans).</p>
<p>For installation procedures, see <a href=3D"https://deepwiki.com/ai-fore=
ver/gigacheck/2-getting-started" class=3D"text-neutral-300 hover:text-neutr=
al-200 hover:underline">Getting Started</a>. For detailed model architectur=
e information, see <a href=3D"https://deepwiki.com/ai-forever/gigacheck/5-m=
odel-architecture" class=3D"text-neutral-300 hover:text-neutral-200 hover:u=
nderline">Model Architecture</a>. For training procedures, see <a href=3D"h=
ttps://deepwiki.com/ai-forever/gigacheck/4-training" class=3D"text-neutral-=
300 hover:text-neutral-200 hover:underline">Training</a>.</p>
